author: John Gillooly
title: Peri Sheinin wins third straight girls tennis championship
text: Peri Sheinin wins third straight girls tennis championship PAWTUCKET – East Greenwich High junior Peri Sheinin won her third Interscholastic League girls state singles tennis title Sunday as she posted a 6-4, 6-0 victory over Wheeler School sophomore Julia Pezzuco at Slater Park.More to come.
